page.title: 06Norton & Lenchwick People
page.content: On 4.7.85 2 children did these activities: Vicky Evans.At 07.00 she got up.She had Frosties and milk for breakfast. Lunch:meat sandwiches,apple,caramel wafer.Dinner:Meat,potatoes,gravy.She watched T.V am. and Dramarama. She read the "Wizard of Oz".She went to school.She played with Amanda,Jane and Sally. Lisa Johns.At 07.00 she got up.She had Rice Krispies and milk for breakfast. Lunch:meat sandwiches,apple,biscuit. Dinner:faggots,chips,peas.She watched T.V am. and Cartoon Time. She read "Look in".She went to school.She went to Cheltenham in the evening.She bought crisps and an apple.She played with Lorraine,Deborah and Amanda.
